sources.description:
It's Friday@PizzaFLIX 
CAPTURED LIVE on KINOSCOPE!
Starring: James Dean, Betsy Palmer, Gene Lyons
Director: Matt Harlib
üçïSTUDIO ONE Season 5 Episode 46üçï
James Dean delivers a compelling performance as a troubled youth accused of murder. After a witness misidentifies him as the killer, the stakes rise as the date of his execution approaches. 

TRIVIA: Studio One began as a CBS radio drama in the 1940s and was reborn as a television series in 1948. It became the longest-running one-hour dramatic anthology in television history!
